### BASICS
F1 - Focus Source
SHIFT+F1 - GO to definition
F2 - Focus Console
SHIFT+F2 - Focus console output
F3 - Focus help
SHIFT+F4 - Go to function help
CTRL+SHIFT+F3 - Help Search
ALT+SHIFT+F3 - help back
ALT+SHIFT+F4 - help forward
F4 - Focus Files
SHIFT+F4 - Go to source file location in files pane
CTRL+ALT+SHIFT+F4 - Focus find in files

### STYLE
F6 - style active file
SHIFT+F6 - style package
CTRL+SHIFT+F6 -  style selection
F7 - check spelling

### ANALYSIS WORKFLOW
F11 Create function definition on clipboard
F17 - Load Drake Project
F18 - Run drake::r_make()
SHIFT+F18 - Visualize workflow
F19 - Loadd at cursor
SHIFT+F19 - Loadd targets for function
F21 - restart R session
SHIFT+F21 - restart RStudio

### SOURCE BROWSING
Shift/ctrl instead for hard
DEL+Alt - Delete from cursor to EOL
BKSPC+Alt - Delete from SOL to cursor
CTRL+DEL/BKSPC - Remove right/left word
L+Alt - Fold
L+Alt+Shift - Unfold
G+Alt+Shift - go to line
J+Alt+Shift - browse sections
Split into Lines
CTRL ALT A
Split line CTRL J

##### Find
Ctrl+F - Find
Ctrl+K - Find Next
Ctrl+Shift+K - Find Previous

### PACKAGES
SHIFT+F14 - Open roxygen quick reference
CTRL+ALT+SHIFT+R - insert roxygen skeleton

